EIF.Label: Entry into force
EIF.Labeltext: 1 October 1991, in accordance with paragraphs 4 and 5 of Resolution No. 352. The Agreement was extended on 1 October 1992 by Resolution No. 355 adopted by the International Coffee Council on 27 September 1991 [see chapter XIX.25 e)].

TreatyText.Label: Text
TreatyText.Text: United Nations, Treaty Series, vol. 1651, p. 572; Resolution No. 352 adopted by the International Coffee Council.
